Megan Huang is going to be the talk of the comic book world very soon, but until then she was graceful enough to talk to us about her pathway into comics, whether pineapple belongs on pizza, and her journey to creating her OWN comic book published by Dark Horse Comics, Rangers of The Divide! Join us as we talk to one of the brightest new talents to come to comic books and comic book media!  Megan Huang on Social Media Facebook - facebook.com/megan.huang.102 Instagram - @meganhuang5 Twitter - @MeganHuang5 Portfolio -  [https://meganhuang.artstation.com](https://t.co/8OpzdWjSoF?amp=1) Shop - [meganhuangart.bigcartel.com](https://t.co/2M8xAtoE23?amp=1) [\*\*Preorder Rangers of The Divide](https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3007-933/Rangers-of-the-Divide-1) \*(Preorder Code MAR210251) As always, please leave us a review on [ITunes,](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! Please [SUPPORT US ON PATREON](http://Patreon.com/CBCClubhouse)!

